name: Newt
description: The unofficial meme mascot of Neutron, it was launched by an anonymous fan of Neutron. Since inception it has been adopted as the unofficial mascot of Neutron. It has been immortalized in numerous NFT collections across the cosmos. Has over 5% of the supply staked in the DAO via it's community. It has a Max, Total and Circulating Supply of 21,000,000 NEWT. It's known for charmless puns, and culture.
